1
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:29,039
Now, only the Queen Mother can save you.

2
00:01:30,039 --> 00:01:32,960
As long as we pass these 99 steps of the heavenly ladder,

3
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:34,280
we still have a chance.

4
00:01:35,479 --> 00:01:36,520
Did you hear me?

5
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,160
Husband.

6
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,890
These characters are too difficult to write.

7
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,760
I might as well go practice the zither and pipa.

8
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,240
Writing Han clerical script on bamboo slips

9
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,400
is different from writing it on Xuan paper.

10
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,400
As the saying goes,

11
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,800
a rope saws through wood,

12
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,000
and dripping water pierces a stone.

13
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,480
Where there is a will,

14
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,360
there is a way.

15
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,440
You're such a bookworm.

16
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:58,090
Seeing you look so serious and anxious

17
00:02:58,600 --> 00:02:59,930
is actually quite cute.

18
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,240
Yuyao.

19
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,600
The broad peaks

20
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:28,000
reflect the snow's brilliance.

21
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:29,960
The jade pool

22
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,090
ripples with gentle green.

23
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:35,600
The blooming lotus holds a millennium of love,

24
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:39,440
never to be broken.

25
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,640
What a beautiful poem.

26
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:46,200
M-My lady.

27
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:47,760
Who are you?

28
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:48,160
You...

29
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,780
It is improper for men and women to touch.

30
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:55,340
You don't remember me.

31
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:55,960
Miss,

32
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,320
please behave yourself.

33
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,000
It's fine.

34
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,720
It doesn't matter if you don't remember.

35
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:40,380
Missing this lifetime won't make a difference.

36
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:41,880
Sinian.

37
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,770
This is the only lifetime left.

38
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,480
We've survived 98 lifetimes.

39
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,440
In this lifetime,

40
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,960
we can't have any regrets.

41
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,680
Yuyao.

42
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,000
You are so foolish.

43
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:21,560
Why make yourself suffer like this?

44
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,440
It's the 49th level, Sinian.

45
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:49,960
Sinian, hold on a little longer, Sinian.

46
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,120
Sinian, just hold on.

47
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,880
You're here.

48
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,320
Sinian.

49
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:05,890
Young Master Lu.

50
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:13,300
I have never met you before, Miss.

51
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,250
What can I do for you?

52
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,330
You have come from afar.

53
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,680
As the evening drum sounds,

54
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,800
would you do me the honor

55
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,060
of sharing a cup of tea?

56
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,200
Thank you.

57
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:26,020
I received a letter from home.

58
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:28,640
The situation is unstable, and war is raging.

59
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,880
I have studied for ten years.

60
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,400
Now it's time to serve in the army.

61
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:31,960
I

62
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:34,360
wish to emulate Ban Chao of the Eastern Han,

63
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,920
and cast aside the pen to join the army.

64
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,380
I must hurry on my journey.

65
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,730
I will take my leave now.

66
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,320
Sinian.

67
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:53,040
War is merciless.

68
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,400
You must return safely.

69
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:03,760
Lu Sinian,

70
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,780
will you leave me in this life?

71
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,280
I won't.

72
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:08,760
That day,

73
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,480
I saw you clearly,

74
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,520
and decided

75
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:15,240
never to leave your side.

76
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,960
I saw you clearly too.

77
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:17,720
Yuyao.

78
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,440
If one day I really leave,

79
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,170
just crack the whip,

80
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,520
and I will return.

81
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:24,930
Okay.

82
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:25,600
Hiyah!

83
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:26,480
Hiyah!

84
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,840
Sinian.

85
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,600
Sinian.

86
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:44,840
What exactly did we do wrong?

87
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:54,320
Would the best beginning

88
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,320
have been never meeting at all?

89
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:00,520
You stay in the Heavenly Realm

90
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:02,440
and be a good divine official.

91
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:07,140
I will stay in the mortal realm and guard the Jade Pool well.

92
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:13,320
That way, we can both live well.

93
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,200
Sinian.

94
00:10:33,760 --> 00:10:35,280
I tried my best.

95
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:41,080
I really tried my best.

96
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:45,800
Yuyao.

97
00:10:58,560 --> 00:10:59,420
Your Highness,

98
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:03,480
please save Sinian.

99
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,720
Yuyao,

100
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,240
for him,

101
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:09,480
you trespassed on the Heavenly Ladder,

102
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:11,280
violating the Heavenly Laws.

103
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,440
Is it really worth it?

104
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,280
I owe him.

105
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:20,640
I will repay him with ninety-nine lifetimes.

106
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:24,240
I have no regrets.

107
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:27,900
Your Highness.

108
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,560
You promised me that

109
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,840
as long as we pass these 99 trials,

110
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:37,120
you would let us be together forever.

111
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,640
In this world,

112
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,130
is there anything that can be eternal?

113
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:43,920
Like you,

114
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,680
I once met someone.

115
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:47,880
At first,

116
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:51,320
I also thought it was love.

117
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:54,600
But

118
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:57,480
he lied to me.
